###  http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#SpatialObjectCollection
GeoSPARQL:SpatialObjectCollection rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                  rdfs:subClassOf rdfs:Container ,
                                                  [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
